{"word":"ἀθώπευτος","slug":"ἀθώπευτος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀθώπευτος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:θωπεύω'><el>θωπεύω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>not flattered, without flattery</i>, <el>τῆς ἐμῆς γλώσσης</el> <i>from</i> my tongue, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <i>not flattering, discourteous</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}